{"tid":728794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"温哥華無車日活動推出「健康飲品」熱狗水？","createTime":"2018-07-04T04:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T06:48:11.000Z","uid":31314,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"960dc9525bb2e9b73103c17d360bb9d9dc792034","tid":728794,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"上星期加拿大温哥華無車日（Car Free Day）活動的一個「健康飲品」攤檔便再一次見證人類可以輕信到甚麼程度。<br />\n<br />\n這個攤檔售賣的是一種名為「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>熱狗水</strong></span>（hot dog water）」的飲品，聲稱飲後<span style=\"color: red;\">可令人減輕體重、增強腦部功能、看起來更年青和更有活力</span>。當然，除了這些空泛的形容，攤檔還貼出一張較詳細的說明，上面有類似科學解釋，並附有兩個見證︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/92oho2V.80N85UnKcaJmcA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thenewslens/a51c207533763d0544afb122cbfbd983\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F92oho2V.80N85UnKcaJmcA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthenewslens%2Fa51c207533763d0544afb122cbfbd983&h=61f5a8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">熱狗水售價是加幣$37.99，約港幣$225</span>；一瓶健康飲品，這個價錢無疑是十分昂貴。那麼，熱狗水的成份是甚麼？不就是名副其實的熱狗和水（hot dog water = hot dog + water），即一瓶清水裏浸著一條熱狗︰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yEBnN7DhRTuuc02zl_lCGQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thenewslens/d9db111eed65c4974cafd083077210f2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyEBnN7DhRTuuc02zl_lCGQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthenewslens%2Fd9db111eed65c4974cafd083077210f2&h=631246d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有沒有人這麼笨，花加幣 $37.99 買一瓶浸著熱狗的清水？有的，而且不少；據檔主說，當天他賣出了約六十瓶熱狗水。從圖片看，這個攤檔的確有人問津︰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_cOLCLBZyPeUgSw56nB1Bg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDcy/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thenewslens/bc7453178baf5419064e6d93a0e9c607\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_cOLCLBZyPeUgSw56nB1Bg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDcy%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthenewslens%2Fbc7453178baf5419064e6d93a0e9c607&h=b1196578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這不過是一個人類行為實驗，目的是看看有多少人會連「熱狗水」這麼荒謬的產品亦會相信可能有效（即使未必完全相信，但願意花相對昂貴的價錢一試，已表示沒有強烈的懷疑）。受騙的人是不是同時買了一個教訓？那要看他們是否知道受騙了，不過，就算知道，也不保證他們下一次不會落入類似的圈套。<br />\n<br />\n印在瓶上的所有文字寫著︰「熱狗水這荒謬之舉，是希望能鼓勵批判思考，令大家意識到產品推銷伎倆如何嚴重地影響我們的購物選擇。」"},{"pid":"341edf0c8b796ede822bef8ada808f92b4c744a6","tid":728794,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c53079a56235ef0cc5dec4f2154cea232f78f7e","tid":728794,"uid":69083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"諗起海灘毒毛蟲養生功效個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ad10afd242c59b3bdb9ee7633a5d406f080ef3","tid":728794,"uid":60333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"如果有咁簡單啲尖房一早執晒笠啦<br />\n成日想不勞而獲咪出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1708862aa4e1f5649093bb4095269bea1d331d69","tid":728794,"uid":86558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"小學果時有人會放m記薯條落水到，等支水有m記薯條味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e33710616478af7feea726f4b59287001985d1","tid":728794,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"抽緊某政治團體？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g